node.text:
You can’t fake this. Tech Deck has been involved in the foundations of skateboarding for a long time. @thenineclub sat down with @devontejolly to talk about skating, starting out, and life. Who started out skating using a Tech Deck? Let us know in the comments with a ❤️

#startsmallgobig
